&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17384666" author="dc-heros" created="Wed, 21 Jul 2021 05:44:32 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;After look closely, I found out that the overflow check in encode is wrong and need to work on too.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;For example:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
scala&amp;gt; spark.sql(select conv(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&apos;aaaaaaa0aaaaaaa0a&apos;&lt;/span&gt;, 16, 10)).show

+-------------------------------+
|conv(aaaaaaa0aaaaaaa0a, 16, 10)|
+-------------------------------+
|           12297828695278266890|
+-------------------------------+&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;which should be 18446744073709551615&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I will raise a pull request soon&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
